<br>
It used to be that as an enchanter, all I'd do when charmed is nuke or maybe root, but since they added mez to the AI, when charmed the game will have me try to mez people as well.<br>
<br>
It could be that the AI &quot;memorizes&quot; spells in a specific order of &quot;spell gem&quot; and weights them that way, meaning it might &quot;prefer&quot; to cast the spell in slot 1 or 8 or whatever, but I don't think it is exclusive.  <br>
<br>
Of course this is mainly conjecture, but doing it that way would let you design a wizard NPC that &quot;preferred&quot; fire magic or &quot;preferred&quot; cold magic pretty easily.<br>
<br>
<br>
